HIM, 
Not a  problem. I've attached the indictment. The other filings are on docket 19 Cr. 490 (RMB)â€” please let me know if 
you'd like me to download anything else. Here are the materials on our website: 
https://www.justice.goviusao-sdny/prheffrey-epstein-charged-manhattan-federal-court-sex-trafficking-minors 
https://www.justice.goviusao-sdnyiprograms/victim-witness-services/united-states-v-jeffrey-epstein-19-cr-490-rmb

As for other items in our possession that are public, we have both a selection of filings from civil cases that we pulled from 
public dockets (though I would not necessarily want to reveal which civil suits we tracked), as well as a copy of the FOIA 
production that FBI Palm Beach produced regarding the initial investigation. 
Thanks, 
From 
Sent: Tuesday, March 10, 2020 6:23 PM 
To: 
Subject: Epstein FOlAs 
further to the little meeting we had a couple weeks ago, could you kindly pull together the Epstein press 
releases and charges and anything else we made public? (I don't think you need to download everything from the 
docket, tho.) 
Associate U.S. Attorney
